
Test Preconditions:
Generate error messages on an employee edit (see   DEM-7 IDEA  if you need directions), taking note of the employee record's original state.

Test Script:
Change one or more fields (in accordance with the requirements laid out in   DEM-1 DONE  )
Click "Save"
Test Postconditions:
Any fields you edited that were in error are no longer underlined and their error message has disappeared.

If all errors have been so addressed, the record is saved as in  DEM-5 IDEA  .